org.openpnp

Interface JobProcessorListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JobProcessorListener.Adapter, NavigationView

    public interface JobProcessorListener
    Allows an interested listener to receive events as the JobProcessor does it's work. Methods in this interface are for passive observers.
